om Eternal is on the right. But I am sure you won’t mistake any.</p>\n<h4 id=\"its-in-the-beginnings\"><a href=\"#its-in-the-beginnings\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>It’s in the beginnings</h4>\n<p>The intro screens are an underappreciated part — usually devoted to seizure warnings or publisher’s commercials. Yet, sometimes they manage to set the mood.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 600 337' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-63fe5f370769c02ec3ca31a5e73105d5'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-63fe5f370769c02ec3ca31a5e73105d5)' width='600' height='337' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bWe%2bj1TDrmoy%2bpeq6A84bSo9tJdrB4LxKZGUtnGeuMZxXNGvk/1FKJNg7mitfxEm39VWHx8/M2r4A/XqgNsTchuZLcaDqfvxxiV4/wzeSoc4YjHA4PP2q8vzeoSeo%2bt6JJOPjINDhuUhCAeMjOwJzjPQAxmui3dbQpoGvXYjUXD6dLE8n/RRUkIH7Asx/muJP2JeSeE57PNKSMxOytnyBwR96yT9GOac%2bMgjGOKw65Oe67sNxrokxL5LUq0hDXEeB0w/uocEmMc1sbJ1jJkLfx96C20er46i9Jlw/VT1R2/sua5Ol2lvf7suLRbdmUgiBMZAkYfck%2bA5P544rjdG9fdE%2bBuL7XNCJ3dHZmxSa2UBLmM8jLHlQDyRz9u8VX1pRKGdwCW5JJ5zQI4vfu0gQEs7BFAxyTwBzWFmpsX6/DMa3t%2bywm8f8g9H%2bLa72nohTcV/bpDd3F4oIhRc4QYP18k46HOTzxW32R6xPvy83FaXix2CfBzPHbNJnzn8AH8M9jCkgd/U3dVXugEndACFUkc91G91o3DozKw6IOCKabbIcvjxK0iO4BUfsKG744FOkbFAJyaVIjyVrhBlJzR4nORzSpVihsTeyUszhQM98UNpG/WlSokkXunrsC7k/nQHY47pUqWSDM2CY5ptKlSoifZ/9k=' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"600\" data-srcset=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/02.bd6740a.77993fdccc169017757b2b5be83e43ba.jpeg 600w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/02.bd6740a.77993fdccc169017757b2b5be83e43ba.jpeg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/02.bd6740a.77993fdccc169017757b