"600\"></noscript>\n<img src=\"./05.jpeg\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"level-selection-loading\"><a href=\"#level-selection-loading\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Level selection &#x26; loading</h4>\n<p>While the difference is not huge, you can see the style — toned vs arcade-like.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 600 337' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-32aa2f7786ff5509313af28a456d994c'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-32aa2f7786ff5509313af28a456d994c)' width='600' height='337' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bWyf2a1Lezm3Nqdyd2gOQOOev/RXKdqijtXS5EIhnEYfdMUPWlTwy7veGMhOWa9aljI8KsYmOo5yRy64p1tsOS%2bjMcFvLIzKW0omo4%2bfDpUj52eyhcJs8DIrqCCDXKOycnYehxW3tLZzxTzQuul4iVcMCpBHTHzrDVCRnFW12Ka0ltq63jPQ2caiNgyg8eePt6VJd2cZYNE2cniM5x%2bqttpWQEKFKn5jNdEADwjNbouEMcYJUMQCvI7wr7UqS2ugxEd2%2bk8gH5CtcTxCGNSGLAEHCKfep9OqbMYwv%2bQPajwGv4Rwy7VHwl2jOEQGQBnJGfyafYbc23sxzcWG1ZI5dJQkac6Tz5%2bla1isUcjGZFbwHSGQMCenA%2b9R3Fsf5pnijjXjqCaBp7cqV1wftIbsmvr/TM2nfX9/dTXG0ZN7czMZHkyPEx68OFT26kgKRWlIgZSZOLVME0vy4famSUViQrk5eW9MVZZBwDHFN3rn%2bx/BoophdZxrbV5m709Wb6m70UUAdBmz5m70NI%2bPO3eiigBLO/wBbd6SzvnzN3oorTD//2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"600\" data-srcset=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/06.bd6740a.3965853af4da319d31b7e216c46acaaf.jpeg 600w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/06.bd6740a.3965853af4da319d31b7e216c46acaaf.jpeg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/06.bd6740a.3965853af4da319d31b7e216c46acaaf.jpeg\" width=\"600\"></noscript>\n<img src=\"./07.jpeg\"></p>\n<p>But once we load a level, the difference is profound: immersing us into the lore, or teaching keyboard shortcut