93c300e'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-678f16217348c8e07931d7a3e93c300e)' width='600' height='337' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bKZSS4MRI22Pz%2baTISDtTeOJprVjg5XcGpWMdlqK9TmKYxzwkn6RpP%2bSa6kuy0j6B28knaoTHmNmBXIPmeK4t4i82WyygfUFJ%2b1FD3K1pZw/Y2s71O/GbhNW43J4/qoJrppL2RmO4GM%2b%2b3zREiY4IYnGpgcAe1VpwElbQSwzyfOjTNi8njtU1my8Czi1luL58ARKTk77/PzSPqvWJg87K7LLIxI34POajgvFt%2bmrDlg0h3IHApXesk0mWyQOD51Shms8930RbGcMDitnYeILC38Kz9PPTInvncMt4WOpV/bjjFY5Bk7KSatrbyiMu0cipzq0nFNry%' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"600\" data-srcset=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/21.bd6740a.b39adf84e67c2a75a6c8b4a9869eddd1.jpeg 600w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/21.bd6740a.b39adf84e67c2a75a6c8b4a9869eddd1.jpeg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/21.bd6740a.b39adf84e67c2a75a6c8b4a9869eddd1.jpeg\" width=\"600\"></noscript>\n<img src=\"./22.jpeg\"></p>\n<p>I DID think that in Doom 2016 life, armor and ammo dropped by enemies was… well, not realistic (do enemies have some ammunition sacks in their bellies?), but after getting used to the convention — immersive nonetheless.</p>\n<p>Now, by comparison, I consider the faded yellow and blue to be a masterpiece of style, compared to, as previously advertised, <em>demon piñata</em>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 600 337' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-761b300fbc0ef18980373402f986466b'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-761b300fbc0ef18980373402f986466b)' width='600' height='337' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2b97Buu00qdzc0AitIDEQRwMA4IHg4IONJNzh