h. In Doom Eternal, well, it is closer to the Mario Bros style.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 600 337' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-1ea4d1385539cfb43cf947304dd1bf6d'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-1ea4d1385539cfb43cf947304dd1bf6d)' width='600' height='337' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2btcE7N2j0YznYA1k9T1C4vJgrzdQJJxviiWbewZnSR5b%2b%2bmwHuTuM4Xb/VMyFzJiWR2P3NPN1gYCxbeopIM2dgn%2bVNw8mRZyJCAzRw59MkZyakpDdSLkoR98DFcRbvoUIqtuSfMKkwDUiPJbOw%2bCP%2b0in2MFvkc7c0SBmiKg%2b%2b1Vd4Oxdsp2V/NseDU6S5muGPcdmNKv9NnuIEdY3AA2YggH4zRrsDNB4J0ew1Jr4XaOxjtmlRY4w7tgbkZI45x7Vj7qMRzP0klDkZFWWhX93pcqsoaN1bGSNjt/H9U7rdydSnErqqEDGwwKw4wJpKABpJNm6fkmlFZ42KsWB9iM0uaMIGBIztg%2b1Fh37kmOAM8iqW6AMnpAyT%2bBVPYu5FRPPgEKD6eoqTHfGI9Ld1COelsgU9YwX5mMcUNxLKQPJGhcsCM48u/Ht/VTdN0OS9uJYIlNtLGC0kUwIZfuOalcDtpSt3%2bRrRJXiu/pnHVsTgGrTT/EWpi7dGuS8T5UxOOpMccHaiihaz%2bU3k1Q3YnXreIRxSKgHUclRx%2bKqmRSzg7hRkUUVOkoynvPPOMngelQlYxyqUJBPtRRXTXyRtLS11W/tj9C7mTHoG2/VPtqN1JcG7eUm446xsf6oooqpjFDOk//2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"600\" data-srcset=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/25.bd6740a.864aa14f02a388a374bfb3154788a54c.jpg 600w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/25.bd6740a.864aa14f02a388a374bfb3154788a54c.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/migdal-blog-gridsome/assets/static/25.bd6740a.864aa14f02a388a374bfb3154788a54c.jpg\" width=\"600\"></noscript>\n<img src=\"./26.jpeg\">\n<img src=\"./27.jpg\">\n<img src=\"./28.jpeg\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"conclusion\"><a href=\"#conclusion\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Conclusion</h3>\n<p>Doom Eternal is a game consistently different in style than Doom 2016. Instead of stylish, immersive minimalism, there is everything added that can be epic (which may make it harder to suspend disbelief) and everything shouts “it is a game!” ad nauseam.</p>\n<p>Yes, you still get as much demonic exposure and savage gore. To some extend I find the dissonance between candy graphics with hue set to max vs internal organs ripped and tore to be similar to that of the Happy Tree Friends… but without due irony.</p>\n<p>While I personally dislike the new style, I am sure that some people like it. To make it clear, I still plan to play it, as for a casual challenge it is fun. Yet, I need to rip and tear the dreams of playing it in one or two fully immersive sittings — at least for me, it is not a game for that kind of experience.</p>\n<h4 id=\"some-otherpeople\"><a href=\"#some-otherpeople\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Some other people</h4>\n<p>While a lot of people praise the game mechanics improvements, I didn’t see nearly as much appreciation for colorful UI. On <a href=\"http://reddit.com/r/doom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Reddit r/doom</a> there are quite a few vocal posts, sharing a similar sentiment:</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 800 900' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-ec976493116820f730c3e4effb38e8cf'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-ec976493116820f730c3e4effb38e8cf)' width='800' height='900' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2b1CinqJkip5IJonLEAHK5Ayem4Grv%2bIq9UlfxpbvcXhk94o0QsjgjIkbv22PfSmTUvbrRByIvgfzwRkcVxF9d1hddGWq2kQBCXyu2Mb6lU07U7CZ44qhseYSIGU7jffWx03AUVb7O7hc4KWaWsppyqr3b9PQY3xntrK%2bJKFrUsUbqUd2bmiYYaMjqrD1309dAYxaTx6pszqHEGlX6qtl8XIWMEDlDKO3y/wCtFb3RVsfDtsqJ4USnkQOjDq2cgE/6ToHUspmbkAVc9Bjb9tHr7djW2ez0Ql5kp6d